  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育平台设计一个完整的静态资源分发架构，核心是ContentCDN服务。学生通过HTTPS访问，流量要经过DNS解析、边缘节点、Lambda处理，最后落到存储上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE",
        "HTTPS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先确认一下层级结构。最顶层是学生端，然后DNS层用Route 53做域名解析，中间是CDN层做边缘加速，最底层是S3存储？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但CDN层不止边缘节点，还要有Lambda@Edge做动态处理，证书管理，以及缓存层。存储层需要OAI来做源站访问身份验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出四个主要区块：学生端、DNS、CDN、存储。CDN层我展开成四个子节点：Edge、Lambda、Cert、Cache。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连接关系需要特别注意：学生先到R53，R53指向Edge，Edge触发Lambda，Lambda验证Cert，然后才到Cache。Cache到存储必须通过OAI，不能直连。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连接画好了。我在Cache到OAI的线上标注了\"OAI Only\"，强调这个安全约束。OAI再连到FILES存储桶。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "R53到Edge那条线，需要明确是A记录还是CNAME？还有Edge到Lambda是触发关系，不是普通连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我简化处理，R53到Edge画实线表示解析指向，Edge到Lambda用触发语义。另外，用户入口我标注HTTPS协议。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "HTTPS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
