    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我注意到节点标签有问题。USER节点显示的是Education_StudentDB，这不对，学生端应该是访问入口，不是数据库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER"
