      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，Education_StudentDB是命名空间前缀，实际角色由位置和连接决定。那CERT节点是Education_ContentCDN，这个是对的？",
      "elements_involved": [
