      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "结构基本完整了。我再确认一下流向：学生→R53→Edge→Lambda→Cert→Cache→(OAI Only)→OAI→Files。整个链条是单向的，没有回流？",
